        <div class="beach">
            <img src="baga-beach.jpg" alt="Baga Beach">
            <h3>Baga Beach (Goa)</h3>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> North Goa, India</p>
            <p><strong>Best Time to Visit:</strong> November to February</p>
            <p><strong>Activities:</strong> Water sports, sunset cruises, nightlife</p>
            <p><strong>Description:</strong> Baga Beach is famous for its vibrant nightlife, stunning sunset views, and
                water sports. It is one of the busiest and most popular beaches in Goa.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Beach 2: Marina Beach -->
        <div class="beach">
            <img src="marina-beach.jpg" alt="Marina Beach">
            <h3>Marina Beach (Chennai)</h3>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India</p>
            <p><strong>Best Time to Visit:</strong> November to February</p>
            <p><strong>Activities:</strong> Morning walks, horse rides, visiting monuments</p>
            <p><strong>Description:</strong> Marina Beach is the longest urban beach in India. Itâ€™s perfect for morning
                walks, enjoying the sea breeze, and exploring nearby attractions.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Beach 3: Varkala Beach -->
        <div class="beach">
            <img src="varkala-beach.jpg" alt="Varkala Beach">
            <h3>Varkala Beach (Kerala)</h3>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> Varkala, Kerala, India</p>
            <p><strong>Best Time to Visit:</strong> September to March</p>
            <p><strong>Activities:</strong> Paragliding, yoga retreats, Ayurveda</p>
            <p><strong>Description:</strong> Varkala Beach is known for its stunning cliffs and golden sand, making it a
                top destination for relaxation and spiritual retreats.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Beach 4: Radhanagar Beach -->
        <div class="beach">
            <img src="radhanagar-beach.jpg" alt="Radhanagar Beach">
            <h3>Radhanagar Beach (Andaman)</h3>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> Havelock Island, Andaman & Nicobar Islands, India</p>
            <p><strong>Best Time to Visit:</strong> October to May</p>
            <p><strong>Activities:</strong> Snorkeling, swimming, exploring nearby islands</p>
            <p><strong>Description:</strong> Radhanagar Beach is known for its pristine sand and clear water, considered
                one of the best beaches in Asia for snorkeling and swimming.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Beach 5: Palolem Beach -->
        <div class="beach">
            <img src="palolem-beach.jpg" alt="Palolem Beach">
            <h3>Palolem Beach (Goa)</h3>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> South Goa, India</p>
            <p><strong>Best Time to Visit:</strong> November to February</p>
            <p><strong>Activities:</strong> Kayaking, dolphin watching, yoga</p>
            <p><strong>Description:</strong> Palolem Beach is a serene and scenic location, perfect for a relaxing time,
                kayaking, and dolphin watching.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Beach 6: Puri Beach -->
        <div class="beach">
            <img src="puri-beach.jpg" alt="Puri Beach">
            <h3>Puri Beach (Odisha)</h3>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> Puri, Odisha, India</p>
            <p><strong>Best Time to Visit:</strong> October to March</p>
            <p><strong>Activities:</strong> Pilgrimages, swimming, beach festivals</p>
            <p><strong>Description:</strong> Famous for its cultural significance, Puri Beach offers a combination of
                spirituality and scenic beauty, along with the chance to enjoy local festivals.</p>
